Core Classes to Search For

ACharacter / APawn → Base player/AI character class.

APlayerController → Handles player input, aiming, HUD updates.

AWeapon / AActor-derived weapon classes → Fire logic, recoil, spread.

UUserWidget → Radar, crosshair, ESP overlays in Unreal Motion Graphics.

AGameState / AGameMode → Match rules, timers, player lists (can be used for radar data).
